Program: The Why Factor
Title: How the Rest of the World Sees America
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03rsqk6
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 2 May 2016
Mike Williams asks what the rest of the world thinks of the United States, one of the most recognisable nations on the planet. This is the second part of a programme looking into the concepts of identity for the BBC World Service's Identity season. (Photo: The American Flag. Credit: Spencer Platt/Getty Images) Show less